article.headline: Dartmouth defeats Sacred Heart 81-76
article.description: — Cade Haskins scored 20 points as Dartmouth beat Sacred Heart 81-76 on Saturday.
article.story: HANOVER, N.H. -- — Cade Haskins scored 20 points as Dartmouth beat Sacred Heart 81-76 on Saturday. Haskins shot 5 for 12 (5 for 11 from 3-point range) and 5 of 9 from the free-throw line for the Big Green (2-0). Jackson Munro scored 19 points while finishing 8 of 11 from the floor and added eight rebounds. Ryan Cornish shot 3 for 9 (1 for 4 from 3-point range) and 7 of 10 from the free-throw line to finish with 14 points. Anquan Hill finished with 20 points for the Pioneers (0-3). Aidan Carpenter added 13 points and four assists for Sacred Heart. Fallou Gueye also had 12 points and two blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
